MintDscTest
├── when amount is zero
│   └── it should revert
└── when amount is greater than zero
    ├── given user has no collateral
    │   └── it should revert
    ├── given user has insufficient collateral
    │   └── it should revert
    └── given user has enough collateral
        ├── when mint fails
        │   └── it should revert
        └── when mint succeeds
            ├── it should record the minted DSC as user debt
            ├── it should credit user with DSC tokens
            └── it should emit a DscMinted event